Oh, well, that's quite simple.

228
00:14:33,107 --> 00:14:35,905
聘金 私人捐献 特别折扣
Retainers, personal donations, special discounts.

229
00:14:36,067 --> 00:14:38,535
杂项开支 中介费
Miscellaneous outgoings, agents' fees,

230
00:14:38,707 --> 00:14:41,699
