难道腐败也是政府的政策?
Is corruption government policy?

243
00:15:21,947 --> 00:15:25,781
不 大臣 腐败从来就不是政策
No, no, Minister! It could never be government policy!

244
00:15:25,947 --> 00:15:29,576
